== Introduction ==
=== Basic ===
anon-connection-wizard is a python-based application that help users in different Internet environment connect to the Tor network. Specifically, anon-connection-wizard can help users connection to the Tor network with a Tor [[Bridges]], or/and a proxy. It will ask users questions about their network environment, like whether they live in censored areas. And then, it will generate a file called anon-connection-wizard.torrc in the /etc/torrc.d/ directory with the most suitable Tor configurations according to the answers from users.

